{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"round","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/round","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath 참고 문서</a></b>: <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 요소</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 함수</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 축</a>\n</div><p></p>\n<p><br>\n <code>round</code> 함수는 인수로 준 수에 가장 가까운 정수를 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ea.b5.ac.eb.ac.b8","title":"구문","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">round(<i>decimal</i> )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.9d.b8.ec.88.98","title":"인수","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"sect2\">\n  <i>\n   <code>decimal</code></i>\n </dt>\n <dd>\n  정수 처리(round)될 10진수.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.b0.98.ed.99.98","title":"반환","isH3":true,"content":"<p>인수\n <i>\n  <code>decimal</code></i>\n 보다 작거나 크거나 같은 가장 가까운 정수.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a3.bc.ec.9d.98","title":"주의","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>-0.5는 음수 0으로 0.4는 양수 0으로 정수 처리됩니다.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a0.95.ec.9d.98","title":"정의","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-round\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.4</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_.ec.a7.80.ec.9b.90","title":"Gecko 지원","isH3":true,"content":"<p>지원함.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"round 함수는 인수로 준 수에 가장 가까운 정수를 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"round","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"round","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"round","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"round","locale":"p